    {
      "_id": "069c54667c7cc107",
      "name": "The Run & Opposition",
      "type": "text",
      "title": {
        "show": true,
        "level": 1
      },
      "image": {},
      "video": {
        "controls": true,
        "volume": 0.5
      },
      "src": null,
      "text": {
        "format": 1,
        "content": "\n        <p>No opposition in the briefing itself. The team leaves with two leads — Tanner's hideout (<em>Leopard's Den</em>) and the cyberdoc's clinic (<em>Chez Cuca</em>) — and whatever cover the GM issued. Encourage legwork (book p.23) before kicking doors.</p>"
      },
      "system": {},
      "sort": 0,
      "ownership": {
        "default": -1
      },
      "flags": {},
      "_stats": {
        "coreVersion": "13.351",
        "systemId": "sr2e",
