    },
    {
      "_id": "13952bfa35a4e834",
      "name": "Dropping Clues & Debugging",
      "type": "text",
      "title": {
        "show": true,
        "level": 1
      },
      "image": {},
      "video": {
        "controls": true,
        "volume": 0.5
      },
      "src": null,
      "text": {
        "format": 1,
        "content": "\n        <p>Little can go wrong here. Keep the goal clear — <strong>locate Tanner</strong> — and don't let players over-analyse the cover package. If they head for the clinic first, go to <em>Chez Cuca</em>; for the hideout, <em>Leopard's Den</em>.</p>"
      },
